---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

// Rumusan Reusable untuk Kartu Kaca (Pure Glassmorphism)
const glassCardClass = "p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 group shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] flex flex-col justify-between";
const lightGlassClass = "bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 hover:border-white/40";
const darkGlassClass = "dark:bg-black/20 dark:backdrop-blur-2xl dark:border-white/10 dark:hover:bg-black/30 dark:hover:border-white/20";
const combinedGlassCardClass = `${glassCardClass} ${lightGlassClass} ${darkGlassClass}`;

// Rumusan Reusable untuk Label/Tag Kaca agar "melayang"
const glassTagClass = "text-xs font-code px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border shadow-sm backdrop-blur-sm";
const combinedGlassTagClass = `${glassTagClass} text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 bg-white/10 dark:bg-black/10 border-white/20 dark:border-white/10`;

// Colored Haze: Bias cahaya samar khusus untuk kartu AfterlifeOS & BananaDroid pada hover
const coloredHazeBase = "absolute inset-0 z-0 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-10 dark:group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-300 blur-xl";
const afterlifeOSGlow = `${coloredHazeBase} bg-emerald-500`;
const bananaDroidGlow = `${coloredHazeBase} bg-yellow-500`;
---

<Layout title="Pengalaman | Haikal Luthfianino">
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 w-full relative z-10 antialiased">
        <div class="mb-12 border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-900 pb-8 relative z-10">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-black dark:text-white tracking-tight mb-4">Pengalaman & Project.</h1>
            <p class="text-neutral-500">Eksplorasi di ranah low-level system, hardware, dan rekayasa perangkat lunak.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 relative z-10">

            <div class={`${combinedGlassCardClass} relative overflow-hidden group hover:-translate-y-1`}>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="mb-4 flex justify-between items-center">
                        <span class={combinedGlassTagClass}>Work Experience</span>
                        <span class="text-xs font-code text-neutral-500 flex items-center gap-1">
                            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                            5 Bulan
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-emerald-600 dark:group-hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors">Teknisi Komputer (PKL)</h3>
                    <h4 class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 font-medium mb-3">NS Komputer</h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Menjalani Praktik Kerja Lapangan (PKL) dengan fokus pada perbaikan perangkat keras. Bertanggung jawab dalam mendiagnosis masalah komponen komputer/laptop, instalasi sistem operasi, dan memberikan solusi teknis kepada pelanggan.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class={`${combinedGlassCardClass} relative overflow-hidden group hover:-translate-y-1`}>
                <div class={afterlifeOSGlow}></div>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="mb-4 flex justify-between items-center">
                        <span class={combinedGlassTagClass}>Open Source / AOSP</span>
                        <span class="text-xs font-code text-neutral-500 flex items-center gap-1">
                            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                            2023 - 2024
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-emerald-600 dark:group-hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors">Official Maintainer AfterlifeOS</h3>
                    <h4 class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 font-medium mb-3 relative overflow-hidden">Poco F1 (beryllium) <span class="absolute left-0 bottom-0 h-0.5 w-1/4 bg-emerald-500 scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-300"></span></h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Menjadi pengelola resmi (official maintainer) sistem operasi AfterlifeOS berbasis Android. Bertanggung jawab atas kompilasi rutin (build), pengelolaan device tree, pembaruan kernel, perbaikan bug, serta memastikan stabilitas OS untuk pengguna publik.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class={`${combinedGlassCardClass} relative overflow-hidden group hover:-translate-y-1`}>
                <div class={bananaDroidGlow}></div>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="mb-4 flex justify-between items-center">
                        <span class={combinedGlassTagClass}>Open Source / AOSP</span>
                        <span class="text-xs font-code text-neutral-500 flex items-center gap-1">
                            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                            2023
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-emerald-600 dark:group-hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors">Official Maintainer BananaDroid</h3>
                    <h4 class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 font-medium mb-3 relative overflow-hidden">Xiaomi Mi A1 (tissot) <span class="absolute left-0 bottom-0 h-0.5 w-1/4 bg-yellow-500 scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-300"></span></h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Dipercaya sebagai maintainer resmi untuk custom ROM BananaDroid. Mengelola source code, memastikan sinkronisasi repositori berjalan lancar, dan merilis build yang stabil dengan penyesuaian performa khusus untuk arsitektur perangkat.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class={`${combinedGlassCardClass} relative overflow-hidden group hover:-translate-y-1`}>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="mb-4 flex justify-between items-center">
                        <span class={combinedGlassTagClass}>Machine Learning</span>
                        <span class="text-neutral-500 font-code text-xs">AI</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-emerald-600 dark:group-hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors hover:cursor-pointer">Hardware Diagnostics AI</h3>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Pengembangan sistem pakar menggunakan algoritma K-Nearest Neighbor (KNN) untuk mengklasifikasi dan mendiagnosis kerusakan pada komponen motherboard.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
